WEBVTT

1
00:01:13.782 --> 00:01:14.949
Your Majesty.

2
00:01:35.845 --> 00:01:40.767
THE EAST PALACE

3
00:01:42.143 --> 00:01:46.648
Yeom-mae? I cannot hear you. Speak louder.

4
00:01:48.525 --> 00:01:50.860
Why is it so cramped in here?

5
00:01:50.944 --> 00:01:52.821
What am I. some kind of grub?

6
00:01:52.904 --> 00:01:55.115
Is this really the only place
you could hide me?

7
00:01:55.865 --> 00:01:57.158
What is he saying?

8
00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:01.496
Come closer and speak.

9
00:02:01.996 --> 00:02:03.289
Through this hole.

10
00:02:15.844 --> 00:02:18.346
Perhaps I should quit now. Heavens.

11
00:02:18.429 --> 00:02:20.014
Would you stop complaining?

12
00:02:20.098 --> 00:02:23.059
You were the one who chose to stay
when I told you to run.

13
00:02:23.143 --> 00:02:25.854
I stayed because I vowed to save you
the way you saved me.

14
00:02:25.937 --> 00:02:27.480
Are you scolding me now?

15
00:02:28.064 --> 00:02:31.442
I begged my grandmother to hide you.
but you keep complaining.

16
00:02:31.526 --> 00:02:34.445
So I am about to lose
all sense of guilt and gratitude.

17
00:02:34.946 --> 00:02:36.698
Yeom-mae…

18
00:02:41.119 --> 00:02:42.787
is difficult work by nature…

19
00:02:44.873 --> 00:02:46.666
so I lost my temper for a moment.

20
00:02:46.749 --> 00:02:48.418
So…

21
00:02:51.379 --> 00:02:54.090
what exactly is this yeom-mae?

22
00:02:55.592 --> 00:02:56.509
A cursing ritual.

23
00:02:57.844 --> 00:02:59.554
A most vile one.

24
00:02:59.637 --> 00:03:03.016
A ritual where someone is sealed in a jar
and starved to death…

25
00:03:05.018 --> 00:03:06.936
so they become a won-gwi.

26
00:03:08.062 --> 00:03:11.149
-But if--
-I cannot become a spirit in the water.

27
00:03:11.232 --> 00:03:12.775
So this is the only way.

28
00:03:15.987 --> 00:03:17.280
If you do that.

29
00:03:18.573 --> 00:03:20.533
would the Crown Prince's spirit
be banished?

30
00:03:20.617 --> 00:03:22.076
I have no power to do that.

31
00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:27.373
All I can do is let my soul pass through
this small opening.

32
00:03:28.666 --> 00:03:33.296
Instead. I will find a way to suppress
the power of the Crown Prince's spirit.

33
00:03:34.881 --> 00:03:36.049
Then I will…

34
00:03:37.967 --> 00:03:42.305
persuade Father not to have you killed.

35
00:03:42.931 --> 00:03:46.226
But what if you snap at the King again
and get thrown out?

36
00:03:46.726 --> 00:03:48.728
You both have a terrible temper.

37
00:03:49.979 --> 00:03:53.149
Do not worry.
Just make sure you do not die.

38
00:03:54.400 --> 00:03:56.361
You are the one who should not worry.

39
00:03:57.403 --> 00:04:01.157
Do not follow me to the grave
for trying to help me.

40
00:04:11.501 --> 00:04:12.335
Now. then.

41
00:04:12.835 --> 00:04:15.922
Please seal this hole as well.

42
00:05:20.737 --> 00:05:22.113
<i>Where is he?</i>

43
00:05:22.613 --> 00:05:24.657
I cannot tell you.

44
00:05:25.825 --> 00:05:28.703
Not until you promise not to kill him.

45
00:05:28.786 --> 00:05:30.955
Now that Prince Yeongan is dead.

46
00:05:31.664 --> 00:05:33.833
his role in the palace is over.

47
00:05:33.916 --> 00:05:37.045
The spirit has not been banished yet.
so we still need him.

48
00:05:37.128 --> 00:05:38.629
He has already failed.

49
00:05:39.213 --> 00:05:42.383
I will not give that incompetent wretch
another chance.

50
00:05:42.467 --> 00:05:45.678
It is because you never told him
who the spirit truly was.

51
00:05:51.267 --> 00:05:53.394
You must now acknowledge the truth.

52
00:05:53.478 --> 00:05:57.273
If you kill Gu-cheon to hide
that the Crown Prince is the spirit.

53
00:05:58.441 --> 00:06:00.401
we will soon share Prince Yeongan's fate.

54
00:06:03.988 --> 00:06:06.532
As of this moment.
you are dismissed from the palace.

55
00:06:07.033 --> 00:06:07.950
Leave at once.

56
00:06:08.034 --> 00:06:09.827
I cannot do that.

57
00:06:09.911 --> 00:06:11.454
If you disappear.

58
00:06:11.537 --> 00:06:15.416
there will be no one left to… help him.

59
00:06:16.042 --> 00:06:17.001
Then…

60
00:06:19.837 --> 00:06:22.340
I will reveal
your shameful secret. Father.

61
00:06:22.924 --> 00:06:24.801
There was never any pond spirit.

62
00:06:24.884 --> 00:06:27.929
Because you were the one
who killed the late king's son!

63
00:06:34.227 --> 00:06:39.315
Unless you wish to die like your mother.
never speak those words again.

64
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:41.359
Where is he?

65
00:06:44.529 --> 00:06:46.280
So was it you. Father?

66
00:06:48.116 --> 00:06:51.119
-Did you kill my mother as well?
-I will ask you again.

67
00:06:51.702 --> 00:06:54.580
-Where is Gu-cheon?
-I will ask you again.

68
00:06:56.999 --> 00:06:58.960
Did you kill Mother?

69
00:07:07.593 --> 00:07:09.137
Chief Eunuch!

70
00:07:10.138 --> 00:07:12.473
Confine the Princess to her quarters.

71
00:07:12.557 --> 00:07:17.353
Keep a close watch
so she cannot take a single step outside.

72
00:07:35.746 --> 00:07:38.916
That ungrateful little bastard.

73
00:07:39.417 --> 00:07:41.377
It is eating it all by itself.

74
00:08:49.737 --> 00:08:51.614
<i>A deep resentment</i>

75
00:08:52.114 --> 00:08:54.242
<i>has reached every corner.</i>

76
00:08:56.953 --> 00:08:59.080
<i>At this rate. the Princess.</i>

77
00:09:00.623 --> 00:09:02.542
<i>the life of the King</i>…

78
00:09:06.087 --> 00:09:07.255
Royal Noble Consort…

79
00:09:08.464 --> 00:09:10.258
Request Royal Noble Consort Sukbin…

80
00:09:26.023 --> 00:09:29.235
Why are you asking
about the late Crown Prince?

81
00:09:29.735 --> 00:09:34.073
Are there any
of the Crown Prince's belongings left?

82
00:09:36.617 --> 00:09:39.120
I hid you at Saeng-gang's request.

83
00:09:39.203 --> 00:09:41.872
and you summoned me here
to say such nonsense?

84
00:09:42.456 --> 00:09:45.835
Your purpose should be to capture
the spirit tormenting His Majesty.

85
00:09:45.918 --> 00:09:47.378
Why would…

86
00:09:50.172 --> 00:09:52.633
the Crown Prince bear such resentment
toward His Majesty?

87
00:09:54.302 --> 00:09:55.303
Are you saying

88
00:09:56.512 --> 00:09:58.431
the one who is cursing the royal family

89
00:09:59.515 --> 00:10:01.017
is the late Crown Prince?

90
00:10:01.100 --> 00:10:01.976
How dare you!

91
00:10:02.059 --> 00:10:04.437
So this is why His Majesty
is looking for you.

92
00:10:05.187 --> 00:10:06.981
Will you lose your granddaughter as well?

93
00:10:08.024 --> 00:10:09.275
At this rate…

94
00:10:11.193 --> 00:10:13.070
your son and granddaughter

95
00:10:14.614 --> 00:10:17.658
will cough up blood and die.
one after the other.

96
00:10:20.536 --> 00:10:25.541
The villagers near Goyang-hyeon
are refusing labor duty. claiming illness?

97
00:10:27.710 --> 00:10:29.170
What illness. exactly?

98
00:10:29.253 --> 00:10:31.631
It appears to be merely a cold.
Your Majesty.

99
00:10:31.714 --> 00:10:35.468
All the able-bodied men have fallen ill.

100
00:10:35.551 --> 00:10:38.304
The village lies beneath a great mountain.

101
00:10:38.387 --> 00:10:40.264
and its cold air brings on such illness.

102
00:10:40.765 --> 00:10:42.850
Your Majesty. what matters is…

103
00:10:43.726 --> 00:10:46.687
Your Majesty.
the seat of the Crown Prince is vacant.

104
00:10:46.771 --> 00:10:49.982
You must appoint
one of the royal kin to the seat.

105
00:10:50.066 --> 00:10:52.693
-There is no time to lose--
-Who do you mean?

106
00:10:54.195 --> 00:10:56.864
You mean the son of Prince Iksang?

107
00:10:57.573 --> 00:11:00.117
Did you not all see him collapse
with your own eyes

108
00:11:00.201 --> 00:11:04.246
at the banquet on the 70th birthday
of the Queen Dowager?

109
00:11:04.330 --> 00:11:07.249
Do you wish me to appoint
such a flawed child as Crown Prince?

110
00:11:07.333 --> 00:11:09.960
It is still too soon
to appoint a Crown Prince.

111
00:11:10.544 --> 00:11:13.005
I am still in good health.

112
00:11:13.089 --> 00:11:16.342
so do not speak such words…

113
00:11:28.938 --> 00:11:30.481
Your Majesty!

114
00:12:36.422 --> 00:12:39.550
You dare go around stirring up trouble
in the palace.

115
00:12:45.014 --> 00:12:46.223
Do you see this?

116
00:12:52.062 --> 00:12:55.274
This Ikseongwan crown was made
for Prince Yeongan.

117
00:12:57.485 --> 00:12:58.944
But that child

118
00:13:00.446 --> 00:13:02.072
is now gone.

119
00:13:03.616 --> 00:13:05.159
All because of you.

120
00:13:08.370 --> 00:13:11.707
I will risk everything to track you down.

121
00:13:11.791 --> 00:13:13.042
I will find you…

122
00:13:15.294 --> 00:13:17.129
and I will…

123
00:13:21.592 --> 00:13:23.052
at all costs…

124
00:13:37.024 --> 00:13:38.651
Damn it.

125
00:13:40.236 --> 00:13:41.821
I should have fled.

126
00:13:42.905 --> 00:13:45.866
The King is combing through the palace?

127
00:13:46.367 --> 00:13:49.870
Has he lost his mind
now that his last son is dead?

128
00:13:49.954 --> 00:13:52.998
It seems he is searching
for a man called Gu-cheon.

129
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:57.795
He failed in his task.
so he should have tried to flee.

130
00:14:01.465 --> 00:14:02.341
As you wish.

131
00:14:08.722 --> 00:14:10.224
How are things in the palace?

132
00:14:12.768 --> 00:14:15.604
The power of the spirit has spread
throughout the palace.

133
00:14:16.230 --> 00:14:18.232
Even I nearly fainted.

134
00:14:19.817 --> 00:14:23.988
The King's life
is now hanging by a thread.

135
00:14:24.488 --> 00:14:27.032
But what troubles me is Gu-cheon.

136
00:14:28.409 --> 00:14:31.245
I fear he may become a lifeline
for the King.

137
00:14:33.247 --> 00:14:35.791
Then we should

138
00:14:36.750 --> 00:14:39.420
cut that lifeline. should we not?

139
00:14:50.264 --> 00:14:54.518
Your Highness.
His Majesty urgently summons you.

140
00:14:55.936 --> 00:14:59.148
I thought I was not to take a single step
outside my quarters.

141
00:14:59.773 --> 00:15:02.067
His Majesty intends to leave the palace
for a short while.

142
00:15:03.360 --> 00:15:05.696
He wishes you to accompany him.

143
00:15:36.936 --> 00:15:38.020
Halt.

144
00:15:41.065 --> 00:15:43.025
-Check the surroundings.
-Yes. sir.

145
00:15:48.072 --> 00:15:49.156
Very well.

146
00:15:54.078 --> 00:15:55.162
Your Majesty.

147
00:15:56.664 --> 00:16:00.668
They look like refugees with the elderly
and children among them.

148
00:16:01.210 --> 00:16:02.962
It appears they stay here

149
00:16:03.045 --> 00:16:05.089
because their illness worsened
while fleeing.

150
00:16:06.048 --> 00:16:09.218
-It is close to Goyang-hyeon--
-I will see them myself.

151
00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:10.386
Yes. Your Majesty.

152
00:16:37.705 --> 00:16:39.123
Goyang-hyeon…

153
00:16:41.458 --> 00:16:43.419
I should look around the nearby villages.

154
00:16:44.294 --> 00:16:47.423
-Then the memorial rite…
-We will stop by before performing it.

155
00:16:48.382 --> 00:16:51.552
Were you intending to go to the tomb
of the late Crown Prince?

156
00:16:53.846 --> 00:16:55.764
We will perform a rite there.

157
00:16:55.848 --> 00:16:58.559
So did you mean to kill Gu-cheon.
trusting in the rite?

158
00:16:59.435 --> 00:17:03.105
It will not work.
You will need Gu-cheon in the end.

159
00:17:03.188 --> 00:17:06.984
-You must spare his life.
-You two stay here and tend to the people.

160
00:17:07.484 --> 00:17:08.318
To the village.

161
00:17:20.205 --> 00:17:23.083
Come on. you need to eat something.

162
00:17:23.167 --> 00:17:24.168
Sir.

163
00:17:24.668 --> 00:17:25.878
Sir!

164
00:17:25.961 --> 00:17:27.046
No.

165
00:17:27.588 --> 00:17:28.672
Sir.

166
00:17:29.923 --> 00:17:31.967
Please save my Gi-dong's mother.

167
00:17:32.051 --> 00:17:35.763
The blisters have spread up to her throat.
and her whole body is burning like fire.

168
00:17:35.846 --> 00:17:37.890
What am I to do?

169
00:17:38.390 --> 00:17:41.393
Please save her!

170
00:17:41.477 --> 00:17:43.062
There is nothing I can do.

171
00:17:44.938 --> 00:17:46.648
Stay with me!

172
00:17:46.732 --> 00:17:48.609
My dear!

173
00:17:55.574 --> 00:17:56.909
A strange pestilence.

174
00:17:56.992 --> 00:17:58.535
Is there no way

175
00:17:59.161 --> 00:18:00.621
to cure it?

176
00:18:01.205 --> 00:18:02.206
There is none.

177
00:18:02.915 --> 00:18:04.833
I do not even know what illness it is.

178
00:18:05.793 --> 00:18:10.631
When one falls ill. the entire family
is stricken by the next day.

179
00:18:14.718 --> 00:18:18.222
Now every household
is boiling peach branches to drink.

180
00:18:18.764 --> 00:18:20.849
They say a spirit brought the illness.

181
00:18:25.479 --> 00:18:28.440
My lord!

182
00:18:30.067 --> 00:18:34.321
My lord. please help save my father.

183
00:18:34.988 --> 00:18:36.615
Just like my older brother.

184
00:18:38.242 --> 00:18:39.827
he is not breathing.

185
00:18:39.910 --> 00:18:40.911
What insolence.

186
00:18:44.206 --> 00:18:45.582
Forgive me.

187
00:19:04.810 --> 00:19:06.478
I am so scared.

188
00:19:10.065 --> 00:19:11.108
I understand.

189
00:19:11.191 --> 00:19:14.403
Go and tend to this child and her family.

190
00:19:14.486 --> 00:19:15.404
Yes. Your Majesty.

191
00:19:16.905 --> 00:19:17.906
Come here.

192
00:19:24.163 --> 00:19:25.622
It is an unknown pestilence.

193
00:19:27.082 --> 00:19:28.292
A highly contagious one.

194
00:19:36.842 --> 00:19:38.552
We will return to the palace at once.

195
00:19:39.303 --> 00:19:40.846
What shall we do about the rite?

196
00:19:40.929 --> 00:19:42.097
It will be postponed.

197
00:19:42.598 --> 00:19:45.058
-We must stop the pestilence.
-Your Majesty.

198
00:19:46.310 --> 00:19:49.438
What shall we do
about the villagers dying here?

199
00:19:49.521 --> 00:19:52.733
At this rate.
all the people will be in danger.

200
00:19:53.483 --> 00:19:54.568
Hurry.

201
00:20:12.628 --> 00:20:14.880
This is a poem
written by the Crown Prince.

202
00:20:15.672 --> 00:20:20.844
Ever since he was a child.
he would send me his poems in his letters.

203
00:20:22.221 --> 00:20:25.891
That is the only thing
the Crown Prince left behind.

204
00:20:30.020 --> 00:20:31.188
From now on.

205
00:20:32.731 --> 00:20:35.359
you must do as I say.

206
00:20:40.989 --> 00:20:44.451
<i>Go to the study of the Crown Prince.</i>
<i>remove the latch.</i>

207
00:20:45.827 --> 00:20:47.829
<i>and post the Crown Prince's poem</i>
<i>on the door.</i>

208
00:20:50.916 --> 00:20:53.669
<i>Before his power grows stronger.</i>

209
00:20:54.378 --> 00:20:55.921
<i>he must be sealed.</i>

210
00:21:06.765 --> 00:21:10.727
<i>Find Gu-cheon hiding in the palace.</i>

211
00:21:12.104 --> 00:21:15.065
<i>I will trace his steps</i>
<i>from where he had been.</i>

212
00:21:17.484 --> 00:21:19.528
<i>Even the smallest trace</i>

213
00:21:20.028 --> 00:21:21.280
<i>will lead me to him.</i>

214
00:21:46.513 --> 00:21:47.514
There he is.

215
00:22:16.001 --> 00:22:18.503
-They say they found him in the shrine.
-Very well.

216
00:22:19.004 --> 00:22:19.921
Your Majesty.

217
00:22:22.299 --> 00:22:23.800
They have found Gu-cheon.

218
00:22:28.388 --> 00:22:29.473
Kill him.

219
00:22:30.849 --> 00:22:31.808
No.

220
00:22:31.892 --> 00:22:33.977
Father. you must not.

221
00:22:34.478 --> 00:22:35.896
We need him.

222
00:22:35.979 --> 00:22:37.689
Father. you must not!

223
00:22:37.773 --> 00:22:39.066
You have to spare him!

224
00:22:39.733 --> 00:22:40.984
Father!

225
00:22:43.028 --> 00:22:43.904
Drag him out!

226
00:22:44.613 --> 00:22:45.530
No.

227
00:22:52.913 --> 00:22:54.039
Let go.

228
00:23:12.808 --> 00:23:15.185
No.

229
00:23:27.406 --> 00:23:28.949
Get up.

230
00:23:30.992 --> 00:23:32.119
Let go of me.

231
00:23:33.286 --> 00:23:34.329
I said let go!

232
00:23:36.748 --> 00:23:37.791
Easy now.

233
00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.252
You are far too hasty.

234
00:23:46.425 --> 00:23:47.968
The Buddha is watching.

235
00:23:48.802 --> 00:23:51.388
-Take him somewhere out of sight.
-Yes. sir.

236
00:23:59.646 --> 00:24:02.816
-Everyone will die.
-Lost your senses with death so near?

237
00:24:11.241 --> 00:24:13.160
What are you muttering?

238
00:24:16.329 --> 00:24:18.790
That the King will die.

239
00:24:43.231 --> 00:24:45.692
-Where is His Majesty?
-He is inside.

240
00:24:45.775 --> 00:24:47.027
Is something wrong?

241
00:24:48.195 --> 00:24:49.196
Your Majesty.

242
00:24:54.868 --> 00:24:55.827
Your Majesty.

243
00:24:56.786 --> 00:24:57.662
Your Majesty!

244
00:24:58.288 --> 00:24:59.956
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

245
00:25:02.334 --> 00:25:03.877
Your Majesty!

246
00:25:06.129 --> 00:25:07.756
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

247
00:25:07.839 --> 00:25:10.342
Bring the royal physician! The physician!

248
00:25:10.425 --> 00:25:12.219
-Yes. sir.
-Your Majesty!

249
00:25:12.302 --> 00:25:14.554
Your Majesty!

250
00:25:16.181 --> 00:25:19.851
The King is going to die?

251
00:25:20.435 --> 00:25:25.357
Word has spread throughout the palace
that His Majesty may not last the night.

252
00:25:28.652 --> 00:25:33.782
Just as that vile spirit cursed.

253
00:25:35.492 --> 00:25:40.372
will the royal bloodline be cut off?

254
00:25:41.748 --> 00:25:42.624
Pardon?

255
00:25:43.875 --> 00:25:46.670
Your Majesty. what do you…

256
00:25:50.006 --> 00:25:53.593
Dispatch a man to Prince Iksang.

257
00:26:00.308 --> 00:26:01.601
This is your retribution.

258
00:26:03.270 --> 00:26:06.856
Consider this the price
for the evil deeds…

259
00:26:09.192 --> 00:26:11.653
you committed 30 years ago. Father.

260
00:26:52.861 --> 00:26:54.487
Where is he?

261
00:27:09.794 --> 00:27:11.254
Why are you all standing around?

262
00:27:12.505 --> 00:27:13.923
Untie him at once!

263
00:27:14.007 --> 00:27:15.258
Untie him.

264
00:27:33.026 --> 00:27:35.070
You certainly took your time.

265
00:27:35.153 --> 00:27:36.363
Indeed.

266
00:27:37.322 --> 00:27:38.865
You look awful.

267
00:27:39.658 --> 00:27:41.326
If the King has collapsed.

268
00:27:42.911 --> 00:27:45.497
you cannot be safe either.

269
00:27:47.248 --> 00:27:48.583
Are you all right?

270
00:27:51.419 --> 00:27:53.046
I am fine.

271
00:27:55.924 --> 00:27:57.217
But more importantly.

272
00:27:58.677 --> 00:28:00.845
Father is in critical condition.

273
00:28:01.596 --> 00:28:04.849
Is there any way
to banish the spirit right now?

274
00:28:07.268 --> 00:28:08.561
The body.

275
00:28:09.896 --> 00:28:12.440
The body of the Crown Prince.

276
00:28:39.050 --> 00:28:43.430
Bring the body of the Crown Prince
to the palace at once.

277
00:28:43.513 --> 00:28:45.432
What are you saying. Your Highness?

278
00:28:45.515 --> 00:28:46.558
There is no time.

279
00:28:46.641 --> 00:28:48.560
This is to save Father.

280
00:28:49.561 --> 00:28:52.063
We cannot desecrate a royal tomb.

281
00:28:52.689 --> 00:28:56.860
-That would be high treason--
-I will bear full responsibility.

282
00:28:58.361 --> 00:28:59.738
And once Father awakens.

283
00:28:59.821 --> 00:29:04.534
I will bear the punishment
for insulting the royal house as well.

284
00:29:09.247 --> 00:29:12.876
<i>To banish the spirit.</i>
<i>we need the body of the Crown Prince.</i>

285
00:29:16.171 --> 00:29:19.799
<i>But we must not let the spirit find out.</i>

286
00:29:20.300 --> 00:29:23.720
<i>So we must deceive it using a dead animal.</i>

287
00:29:26.222 --> 00:29:29.768
<i>If we fail to drive it away before dawn.</i>

288
00:29:31.603 --> 00:29:33.813
<i>the King is fated to die.</i>

289
00:29:35.356 --> 00:29:40.069
<i>All that remains is for me</i>
<i>to strike the spirit down with my blade.</i>

290
00:29:47.494 --> 00:29:49.412
Can you truly do it?

291
00:29:50.205 --> 00:29:51.414
In that condition?

292
00:29:51.915 --> 00:29:54.959
I may be half-dead.
but what choice do I have?

293
00:30:00.048 --> 00:30:03.843
Thanks to the King's collapse.
I get some fresh air.

294
00:30:03.927 --> 00:30:06.179
Are you joking at a time like this?

295
00:30:07.013 --> 00:30:10.350
That is why you must not forget
what I told you to do.

296
00:30:13.853 --> 00:30:15.313
Do not worry.

297
00:30:16.689 --> 00:30:18.733
And stop frowning.

298
00:30:21.569 --> 00:30:22.570
Gu-cheon.

299
00:30:32.622 --> 00:30:34.249
You told me before.

300
00:30:35.333 --> 00:30:38.920
That your own life matters
more than that of anyone else.

301
00:30:40.171 --> 00:30:42.465
That you do not want to die
and become an ak-gwi.

302
00:30:43.174 --> 00:30:44.926
That is still true.

303
00:30:50.723 --> 00:30:52.016
Then that is enough.

304
00:31:03.695 --> 00:31:04.904
Do not foolishly…

305
00:31:07.448 --> 00:31:09.576
die for me.

306
00:31:13.288 --> 00:31:14.706
Needless to say.

307
00:32:26.027 --> 00:32:29.989
<i>You must bind the body of the Crown Prince</i>
<i>tightly with this bloodstained rope.</i>

308
00:32:31.950 --> 00:32:34.077
There is one more thing
you must bear in mind.

309
00:32:34.160 --> 00:32:36.245
Bind the door shut with the rope.

310
00:32:37.789 --> 00:32:39.374
<i>And no matter what happens.</i>

311
00:32:39.874 --> 00:32:41.751
<i>do not open it.</i>

312
00:32:44.420 --> 00:32:46.089
<i>If I fail.</i>

313
00:32:47.590 --> 00:32:49.509
<i>you will be the next target.</i>

314
00:33:01.312 --> 00:33:03.106
Insolent wretch.

315
00:33:03.189 --> 00:33:04.649
You are doing this in vain.

316
00:33:13.908 --> 00:33:16.160
Do not meddle in this matter.

317
00:33:17.286 --> 00:33:19.789
I must sever the royal bloodline.

318
00:33:21.082 --> 00:33:22.834
I cannot allow that.

319
00:33:23.459 --> 00:33:26.212
There is someone in this palace
I wish to save.

320
00:33:58.327 --> 00:34:00.329
It is all over now.

321
00:34:10.381 --> 00:34:11.424
What is that?

322
00:34:15.011 --> 00:34:17.472
It does not appear to be a gwi-mae.

323
00:34:19.140 --> 00:34:21.517
Good heavens. I cannot believe this.

324
00:34:22.685 --> 00:34:24.520
Whose presiding deity is this?

325
00:34:25.021 --> 00:34:27.356
Who on earth is interfering?

326
00:34:36.449 --> 00:34:37.825
<i>Very well.</i>

327
00:34:37.909 --> 00:34:42.330
<i>How powerful will the presiding deity</i>
<i>you serve be?</i>

328
00:34:43.539 --> 00:34:45.249
<i>Let us see.</i>

329
00:34:56.719 --> 00:34:58.012
The Crown Prince's spirit.

330
00:36:10.042 --> 00:36:13.629
Not knowing your true identity.
I cannot even send you to the heavens.

331
00:36:23.973 --> 00:36:28.477
Here we go! The grim elder!

332
00:37:22.657 --> 00:37:24.992
You shaman wretch…

333
00:37:34.961 --> 00:37:36.587
Something is wrong.

334
00:37:40.591 --> 00:37:43.052
Your Highness!

335
00:37:43.135 --> 00:37:44.053
What is it?

336
00:37:44.136 --> 00:37:45.972
Please open the door.

337
00:37:46.055 --> 00:37:48.057
Something terrible has happened
to Gu-cheon.

338
00:37:48.140 --> 00:37:50.518
You need to get to the pond now!

339
00:37:51.102 --> 00:37:52.436
Please hurry.

340
00:37:53.604 --> 00:37:55.231
-Hurry.
-Very well.

341
00:37:55.982 --> 00:37:58.276
Your Highness! Hurry!

342
00:37:59.360 --> 00:38:00.569
Please hurry.

343
00:38:15.960 --> 00:38:17.420
You know nothing.

344
00:38:20.214 --> 00:38:21.424
Nothing at all.

345
00:39:31.369 --> 00:39:32.578
A gwi-mae…

346
00:39:58.896 --> 00:39:59.772
Enough.

347
00:40:01.690 --> 00:40:03.067
That is enough!

348
00:43:42.244 --> 00:43:45.497
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang
